data.description: Wonderful 4BR/2.5BA, 4-level split level on a quiet cul-de-sac in very desirable Highland Stone in the Beverly Farms/Hoover/Churchill district! This gem features a beautiful, nearly flat lot with fencing around the expansive, play-encouraging yard and rear terrace.  The interior has a welcoming entry hall with coat closet, a large, table-space kitchen with bay window, updated appliances and Corian counters with a side door, sizable dining room overlooking the rear yard, beautiful living room, 4 bedrooms (each with nice closet space and ceiling fans), a hall bathroom with two sinks and a tub/shower and a primary bathroom with a shower stall, a lower level with huge laundry room, half bathroom and entertainment-friendly family room with built-in shelving and wood-burning fireplace with glass doors that opens to the rear terrace and gorgeous yard and a lower level that includes a spacious recreation room and large utility/storage room.  Based on how quickly 8706 Liberty, 8836 Tuckerman and 11814 Coldstream sold last fall, this one will be well received by buyers, as it's much superior to all of those!
